      "name": "Relative Hemolysis Index Comparison — 5 Operating Points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) compared against in-vitro measurements at five flow-speed combinations. RH < 1 for all tested conditions, meeting the acceptance criterion. Mesh independence verified at three refinement levels.",
