      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD-predicted RH index must agree with experimental measurements within 15% at each operating point.",
      "rationale": "Pairwise comparison of CFD and experimental RH values at all five operating points shows maximum deviation of 11.3%. Systematic over-prediction of 4–8% noted at higher flow rates, consistent with turbulence model limitations at transitional Reynolds numbers."
    },
