    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 given medium model influence and Class II device classification. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. RH < 1 criterion met at all five operating points. Assessment team accepts the model for the stated context of use.",
